{"id":1026,"date":"2021-04-16T11:06:05","date_gmt":"2021-04-16T15:06:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/?p=1026"},"modified":"2024-09-15T08:03:56","modified_gmt":"2024-09-15T12:03:56","slug":"case-teaching-highs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/case-teaching-highs\/","title":{"rendered":"Case Teaching Highs"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-1028\" src=\"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/vlcsnap-2021-04-16-14h24m51s137-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"440\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/vlcsnap-2021-04-16-14h24m51s137-2.png 732w, https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/vlcsnap-2021-04-16-14h24m51s137-2-218x300.png 218w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" \/> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-1029\" src=\"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/amar-in-Aldrich-7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"254\" height=\"256\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/amar-in-Aldrich-7.png 212w, https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/amar-in-Aldrich-7-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/amar-in-Aldrich-7-50x50.png 50w, https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/amar-in-Aldrich-7-125x125.png 125w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 254px) 100vw, 254px\" \/>In less than nine months, I\u2019ve put 15 case studies through the HBS system, which may be a record for a single submitter. (About 10 were reconfigured working papers, but they still had to be turned into a teaching product.)<\/p>\n<p>As of next Thursday, I had hoped to have taught all 15 in my Transformational Medical Innovations course. (Teaching a new full credit elective with all new cases might be a record too).<\/p>\n<p>Regardless, yesterday&#8217;s class upset the plan. I assigned two cases &#8212; and invited a superstar cancer researcher Michel Sadelain, as the guest for the first of them. I thought I\u2019d teach the case for about 45 minutes, turn it over to Michel for 15-20 minutes and then move on to the next case. (I had been told Michel didn\u2019t have much time).<\/p>\n<p>About 30-40 minutes into the case discussion, I asked Michel if he could stay a little bit longer.<\/p>\n<p>He said he was finding the discussion fascinating so I should take as long as I liked.<\/p>\n<p>Long story short. Never got to the second case. And Michel was inspirational. Just stellar.<\/p>\n<p>And it may be the best class I have ever had. It is a high that&#8217;s hard to describe.<\/p>\n<p>The other guests and classes have been uppers as well.<\/p>\n<p>I am one lucky dude to have had this chance, if only once.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In less than nine months, I\u2019ve put 15 case studies through the HBS system, which may be a record for<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":true,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"colormag_page_container_layout":"default_layout","colormag_page_sidebar_layout":"default_layout","footnotes":"","_links_to":"","_links_to_target":""},"categories":[31,45],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1026","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-health-blog","category-transformational-innovations"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1026","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1026"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1026\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1031,"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1026\/revisions\/1031"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1026"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1026"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/bhide.net\/wordpress_files\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1026"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}